s that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Administrator requirements Ability to type 50+ WPM Associate's degree required Proficiency in Microsoft Word and Excel Excellent communications skills Organizational skills Maintain office records Administrator related job titles: Executive Assistant Office Manager Receptionist Office Administrator Office Support Specialist Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
